'''飓风妮科尔'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Nicole}}）是1998年大西洋飓风季形成的最后一场飓风，系统于11月24日经[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以南的锋面低气压区发展而成，然后在朝[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向移动期间快速增强至每小时110公里风速。逐渐进入系统上空的上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]产生强烈[[风切变|风切变]]，导致妮科尔很快降级成热带低气压。

低压槽过去后，气旋因外界大气环境中的风切变减少而稳步增强。受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响，妮科尔转向东北，并在进入[[海面温度|水温]]异常温暖的洋面后达到飓风标准。12月1日，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]135公里的最高强度，然后在北大西洋上空迅速减弱直至消散。截至2015年，有纪录以来在12月存在的大西洋飓风还只有5场，妮科尔便是其中之一。

== 源起 ==
{{storm path|Nicole 1998 track.png}}
1998年11月下旬，[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以南数百英里海域有几乎没有移动的锋面低气压区持续存在。系统开始稳步朝西移动，中心附近发展出紧密包裹的[[对流|对流]]带，估计系统于11月24日在亚速尔群岛[[热拉斯_(普拉亚达维多利亚)|热拉斯]]（{{lang|en|Lajes}}）以南约1165公里洋面发展成本季第十四号热带低气压。气旋在朝[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]方向前进期间快速强化，仅成形6小时后就升级成热带风暴并获名“妮科尔”（{{lang|en|Nicole}}）。<ref name="tcr" />风暴的规模很小，其热带风暴强度风场半径在刚升级时仅有95公里<ref name="nicole1">{{cite report | author = Lawrence | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Public Advisory One | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193453/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/pub/PAL1498.001 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/pub/PAL1498.001 | date =  }}</ref>。

达到热带风暴强度数小时后，气旋中心以北不远处经过的一艘船只测得每小时66公里风速，确认系统已属热带风暴。受北侧的强烈中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响，妮科尔继续朝西南偏西方向移动，其中心则位于大规模上层低气压区以内。这片低气压区在风暴上空产生少量[[风切变|垂直风切变]]，对于飓风季末期亚热带海域的天气系统来说，这种情况十分常见。<ref name="tcr" />气旋行经海域水温约为25[[摄氏度|℃]]，因此快速增强，中心有小规模深层对流组成的[[风眼|眼状特征]]，风速达到每小时115公里的第一波高峰<ref name="pasch3">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Three | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.003 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192930/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.003 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。在此强度下保持约12小时后，有上层低压槽快速向东行进至妮科尔上方，产生强烈风切变<ref name="tcr" />。风暴因此减弱，其中心到11月25日晚已从逐渐消退的深层对流西侧暴露出来<ref name="pasch7">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Seven | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214926/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.007 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。受风切变影响，气旋的大部分对流都已消散，妮科尔因此于11月26日降级成热带低气压，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]此时停止针对系统发布公告<ref name="tcr" />，认为气旋已不大可能再生<ref name="pasch9">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Nicole Discussion Nine | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191828/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.009 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.009 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

== 再生 ==
[[File:NicoleNRL98.jpg|right]]
低气压区转向西进，经过低压槽后，妮科尔上空有高压脊成形，导致风切变减少，风暴上空重新发展出深层对流<ref name="tcr" />。美国国家飓风中心于11月27日重新开始针对[[加那利群岛|加那利群岛]]西南偏西方向约2440公里海域的妮科尔发布公告。下层环流起初从对流西南一侧暴露出来，<ref name="jarvinen11">{{cite report | author = Jarvinen | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Depression Nicole Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.011 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203511/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.011 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>但风暴还是迅速强化，并于11月27日晚出人意料地再度达到热带风暴强度。妮科尔的中心接下来由对流包裹起来，上空还发展出[[反气旋|反气旋]]。系统开始发展[[雨带|带状特征]]，外流层次分明。<ref name="jarvinen12">{{cite report | author = Jarvinen | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Twelve | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224747/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.012 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.012 | date =  }}</ref>受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响，风暴转向北上，于11月28日到达[[百慕大|百慕大]]东北偏东方向约1800公里洋面，这也是妮科尔移动路线中最偏东面的位置<ref name="tcr" />。

转向东北后<ref name="tcr" />，受逐渐逼近的[[锋_(气象)|锋]]产生的风切变影响，气旋略有减弱，中心位于对流西部边缘附近<ref name="jarvinen16">{{cite report | author = Jarvinen | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Sixteen | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.016 | accessdate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.016 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref><ref name="nicole17">{{cite report | author = Mayfield | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Seventeen | publisher = National Weather Service | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225526/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.017 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.017 | date =  }}</ref>。虽然有风切变的不利影响，但在上层分流的维护下，妮科尔的对流得以持续<ref name="nicole18">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Eighteen | publisher = National Weather Service | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121018162312/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.018 | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.018 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-18 | date =  }}</ref>，对流内还发展出眼状特征<ref name="nicole20">{{cite report | author = Jarvinen | year = 1998 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Twenty | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201456/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.020 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/dis/NAL1498.020 | date =  }}</ref>。风暴因行经洋面水温比正常水平要高2至3℃而得以继续强化，于11月30日清晨在亚速尔群岛热拉斯西南偏西方向约2060公里海域达到飓风标准。风暴内已组织出接近完整的风眼墙，妮科尔于12月1日清晨达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]135公里的最高强度。气旋转向北上并迅速弱化，于当天晚上在亚速尔群岛西北方向约460公里洋面转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。风暴残留沿更大规模环境的边缘向西北方向移动，于12月2日完全消散。<ref name="tcr" />

== 影响和纪录 ==
飓风妮科尔存在期间自始至终距陆地都有数百英里，所以没有造成任何人员伤亡或财产损失<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | year = 1998 | title = Hurricane Nicole Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002012646/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL141998_Nicole.pdf | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL141998_Nicole.pdf | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。

妮科尔在12月达到飓风强度，是有纪录以来仅有的5场12月大西洋飓风之一。另外4场分别是[[1887年大西洋飓风季|1887年]]的无名飓风，[[1954年大西洋飓风季|1954年]]的[[1954年12月飓风爱丽丝|飓风爱丽丝]]，[[1984年大西洋飓风季|1984年]]的[[1984年飓风丽丽|飓风丽丽]]和[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]的[[飓风艾普塞朗|飓风艾普塞朗]]。<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2005-12-02 | title = Hurricane Epsilon Discussion Fourteen | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al292005.discus.014.shtml? | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310082857/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2005/dis/al292005.discus.014.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-10 }}</ref><ref name="Meta">{{Cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181152/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_aug11.html | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2011 | accessdate = 2016-05-03 | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_aug11.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>

